Document: AudioStreamPlayback
Path: godot/classes/class_audiostreamplayback.rst
Summary: Provides methods for playing, pausing, and looping audio streams.

AudioStreamPlayback can play, loop, pause a scroll through audio. See AudioStream and AudioStreamOggVorbis for usage.
